      <title>据彭博社报道，欧舒丹的亿万富翁老板可能提出 70 亿美元的收购报价</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/loccitanes-billionaire-owner-close-possible-7-bln-buyout-bid-bloomberg-reports-2024-04-28/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据彭博社报道，欧舒丹国际公司的亿万富翁老板最早将于周一提出将这家法国护肤品公司私有化的提议，这笔交易包括债务在内，该公司的估值可能约为 70 亿美元。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/loccitanes-billionaire-owner-close-possible-7-bln-buyout-bid-bloomberg-reports-2024-04-28/</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 28 Apr 2024 18:49:13 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
